WEBVTT

00:04.560 --> 00:05.360
Oh!

00:05.360 --> 00:07.680
Aaaahhh! 
 Gary, are you OK?

00:08.480 --> 00:10.640
- Gotcha. 
 - You toad.

00:10.640 --> 00:12.680
GARY: 
 I love that trick.

00:12.680 --> 00:15.280
Yeah, well, you're one 
 sick little puppy, you know that?

00:16.880 --> 00:19.280
So you're dad really owns this place?

00:19.520 --> 00:21.240
Yeah. It's where I get 
 all my story ideas.

00:21.240 --> 00:24.040
There's all sorts of strange, 
 voodoo, and occult stuff in here.

00:24.040 --> 00:29.200
About your stories, Gary-- 
 I shouldn't be telling you this,

00:29.200 --> 00:32.000
but, well... some of 
 the guys have been saying

00:32.000 --> 00:33.720
that they haven't 
 been too scary lately.

00:33.720 --> 00:35.520
Who said that?

00:35.520 --> 00:37.200
I don't know.

00:37.200 --> 00:38.960
What are these?

00:38.960 --> 00:42.120
Super specs. 
 They give you x-ray vision.

00:43.160 --> 00:45.640
- Whoa, yowza! 
 - Give me a break.

00:45.640 --> 00:47.360
What's the matter, 
 you don't believe in magic?

00:47.360 --> 00:50.720
- Oh, and you do? 
 - Maybe I do, maybe I don't.

00:50.720 --> 00:52.840
Sometimes it's best 
 to keep an open mind,

00:52.840 --> 00:55.400
and be ready for surprises.

